name: Search for "Lydia" and open the "Crésus" page in French
fullName: test/features/lydia.feature#Navigate from searching "Lydia" to the "Crésus" page Search for "Lydia" and open the "Crésus" page in French

steps.name: Given the Wikipedia app is installed
When I swipe through the onboarding carousel until the last page
And I scroll the search results until I see the city and dismiss the pop-up
And I change the website language to French
And I scroll to the bottom of the page
Then I should be navigated to the Crésus page
